 word decomposition by calibrating the decision threshold of probabilistic models and using a model ensemble</gtr:title><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/c17b7cd3b2dd1aea127e986c494159a3"><gtr:id>c17b7cd3b2dd1aea127e986c494159a3</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Sebastian Spiegler</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2010-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>r_6020090516cac40b50</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication></gtr:publications><gtr:identifiers><gtr:identifier type="RCUK">EP/E010857/1</gtr:identifier></gtr:identifiers><gtr:healthCategories/><gtr:researchActivities/><gtr:researchSubjects><gtr:researchSubject><gtr:id>EB5F16BB-2772-4DDE-BD6C-3B7A6914B64C</gtr:id><gtr:percentage>100</gtr:percentage><gtr:text>Info. &amp; commun. Technol.</gtr:text></gtr:researchSubject></gtr:researchSubjects><gtr:researchTopics><gtr:researchTopic><gtr:id>41593421-CFAC-411D-94A7-E144022B0E6D</gtr:id><gtr:percentage>100</gtr:percentage><gtr:text>Artificial Intelligence</gtr:text></gtr:researchTopic></gtr:researchTopics><gtr:rcukProgrammes/></gtr:project></gtr:projectComposition></gtr:projectOverview>